cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.CL, cs.DB, cs.CY 

The paper discusses the use of (deep) representation learning for knowledge base completion, which falls under the category of artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG). It also mentions relational learning, which is a subfield of machine learning and falls under the category of databases (cs.DB). The paper also discusses the use of graphs and multi-relational knowledge graphs, which are relevant to natural language processing (cs.CL) and complex systems (cs.CY).
